CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, September 7, 1963, page 3, reads: "First Day - Cathleen Diane Evans, James Anthony Evans and Toni Burrell (arm over head) found their first day at Baxter Elementary School, in Brushton, and interesting if not enjoyable experience. - Harris Photo"
TitMainTitle: Men, women, boys, and girls, including, Cathleen Diane Evans and James Anthony Evans holding hands, and Toni Burrell with arm over head, standing in corridor of Baxter Elementary School
